1 - Essential pieces of functionnel:

- Physical ledger when buying properties - cards
- Monopoly EVM
  - Create Tokens to be utilized as money - Monopoly ETH
  - GRN - To advance in the game
  - Buying properties from the EVM
- P2P transactions
  - Loans
  - Mortgages
  - Paying rents
  - Sell properties

2 - How would people cheat?

- Personal integrity if not enough people / Enough people
- Physically assaulting people to give you there money/properties -
- Printing fake money / Create money / Double spending
- Kill the EVM - Switch off
- Hacking the smart contract and minting tokens.
- Phishing other player's and hacking their wallets.

